flowchart TD
    A[collect_and_compile_event_handlers on DomDocument] --> B[collect_handlers_recursive over DomElement tree]
    B --> C[read on-type attributes onclick onmouseover and so on]
    C --> D[emit wrapper function __evt_handler_N event]
    D --> E{attr is a plain global call}
    E -- yes --> F[append_global_call_inline_handler rewrites to globalThis lookup and call]
    E -- no --> G[inline the raw attribute body verbatim]
    F --> H[concatenate all wrappers into one compile buffer]
    G --> H
    H --> I[transpile_js_to_mir_with_preamble reuses retained heap reusing_context true]
    I --> J[new MIR context deferred not destroyed]
    J --> K[for each element js_property_get wrapper by name]
    K --> L[js_dom_set_event_handler_function installs into on-type IDL slot]
    L --> M[later js_dom_dispatch_event fires with this element and Event arg]
